	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have seen the light!!! <br><br>Previously I could not fathom why anyone would use this SLOOOOOOW casting spell to heal...but when you compare it to minor and even light healing it really makes sense...make sure to keep this and a regular healing spell up...chain casting, and you should chain cast it cause of the slow casting time, this on my tank we took on red crocs and camines in oasis at lvL 8!!! yes lvl 8 just me and an inkie warrior...its a good spell for CONTROLED situations. Dont be affriad to switch to minor or light healing if the hp's are dropping faster than you can cast<br><br>THIS SPELL DOESNT HEAL AT ALL OR STACK WITH CLERIC COURAGE LINE OR DRUID SKIN LINE ARGGG!! make sure to keep another healing spell rdy if someone tosses you resolution or skin like diamond and the like...<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
