	   <tr><td colspan=2>ok im taking this from level 19 where i left off....<br><br>19 spells are decent, affliction does about 180 damage, but in 2 min. healing is good to.&nbsp;&nbsp;at 19, i did the langseax of the wolves quest for a long while, its exelent cash if youre on a newer server, when i did it langseaxes sold for 25p and LoWs sold for 500p, thats how i got a lot of equipment. but for leveling i went to lake rathe and south karana and solo'd avaiks till 24. if you perfer to group go to high hold keep from 22-35. the 24 spells are exelent, new dd, a great dot. at 25 i began soloing tesch mas gnolls outside split paw ( some difficulty at first but then i got the hang of it ) also to do this you should have around 150 wis because they have much much hp.what i did was cast envenemed breath, affliction, then root the gnoll and med until it brakes, then run far and cast DD, and envenemd breath again when it wore off till he was dead.  Gnolls are GREAT exp solo and EXELENT loot. around 25 is when you should start totemic quests, although i use no totemic except the helmut because none of the other adds wisdom ( i used the totemic boots till 45 though when i got e-boots ).also, at 25 look for a spear and work on peirce (it comes in handly later). save for a jade chokadi prod, they cost around 800p on my server. also at level 25 i had the following equipment: blackend iron medallion, gold jasper earings, runed circulet, platinum jasper rings, platinum armband, cloak of the icebear, bloodstained tunic, totemic boots, gatorscale legs, splitpaw hide gloves, chiped bone bracers, enameld black mace, charred gaurdian sheild. stay soling gnolls for a while, you will get lots of cash. at 29 you get healing upgrade, decent buffs, and invis. invis is great, i used it to get to alchemist room in permafrost and camp it forever to get many mammoth cloaks. at 29 it can be very dangerous, so take a friend to be safe  ( wish i did ) just to break spawn or something, if its broken well you can solo it, just keep buffs up, and regen. i got 2 cloaks at 29, one to use and one i traded for a tesch val sinich ( 9/33 4wis 4int 40 range effect poison ). at 34, you get........ A PET!!!!!!!!!! yes a pet! you get a NEW DD, and you also get GREAT buffs, 34 is heaven for shaman, you can solo gnolls with 1 bub of mana! at 35, i went to the bard and killed him, although i wish i hadden because when i forget to invis in qeynos i get mobbed. at 35 i went to lower guk at 35 and soloed for a bit.  this is when i started grouping a lot, in the bedroom in lower guk, i got out of 35 in 10 hours! its extremly good exp in lower guk, i made a level a day from 35-38 in there!<br>at 39, spells are exelent to, venem of snake, scourge, talisman of altune, new pet, more buffs. <br>ok time for another equipment rundown, by now you should probably have a totemic helmut, they cost a lot or you can do the quest, a jade chokadi prod ( 11/33 6wis peirce ) get one of those new belts from paw that adds wisdom, but i had saved up and got a flayed turmoilskin belt. look for some forest loops also. at 39 if you want to solo do trolls in rathe mountains for nice safe exp, decent loot also. if you perfer to group to to executioners roon in lower guk, exelent exp and loot again. at 40, i went to frenzy room for exelent exp, good loot in there but its rare ( flowing black silk sash ). the 44 spells are good, new dd, new pet (this pet is wimpy though) and buffs. at 45 go to solesk b and stay in the window for 15 hours untill you level hehe. at 46 if you want to solo go to specters in ferrot, or trolls in rathe mountains, but i was liking guk very much at this point so i stayed there. from 46-49 switch between frenzy and lord room, you can do exe room from 46-48 but not much exp. at 47 exp it better in lord than frenxy room, but frenxy is MUCH safer.  if you are luckey you will get a FBSS or SMR to trade for e-boots to. the 49 spells KICK SERIOUS ASS! you get e-bolt, a pet that hits for 51 damage, exelent buffs! so right now i am level 49, i solo ice giants now, to do that make pet, buff it up, alacraty pet, togor ice giant, root giant, e-bolt giant, plague giant, and heal pet and re e-bolt when you need, safe, great exp, and they drop about 10 to 50p ( in pp ) with gold and islver and copper each time. when igs are camped go farm permafrost anf get rich heh, thats my guide hope you liked it! if you see me on brell ill be glad to help out, remember wisdom is the most important stat for shamen!<br><br>&nbsp;<br>°=THORGFROSTFIST=°<br>52nd season shaman<br>Brell Serilis<br>Grand Master Drunk</td></tr>
