	   <tr><td colspan=2>Great post! Except for one minor thing....I personally don't like Oasis. All the times i have went there to get exp. I have either died from a spector or sand giant wandering around, or not been able to get many kills becuase it is SOOOO overcrowded. This happened with both my magician and necro characters. If you can get a group and pull in a tons of kills and not get killed by sand giants or spectors, I suspect the exp. might be good.<br><br>Another great spot for level 14-22 for ANY class IMO, is lake rathe. The giant aviaks and the hermit(Jonah) are great exp. The loot on the aviaks isn't bad either(not so hot on Jonah though). There are also orcs and skelatons in the zone which aren't bad. Also, I think a shaman would be able to get from 14 to 18 at one of the double siren spawns in OOT. They are bad loot, but are easy to kill for their level. Since 2 of them spawn every 5 minutes, the exp. is good until then start conning green.<br><br>My highest shaman is only level 10.&nbsp;&nbsp;However from what I have heard from all my shaman friends, and done with my necro and magician, all of these things would be great for a shaman.<br><br>Cool post Thorg....just add to add those for more variety =;-) .<br><br>Corpusnuntia/Divineshadow/Zuranthium/Plantmaster/Naltec/Natalos/Sunsong<br><br>Player of many characters on the Nameless server.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
